  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L52-L64\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L52-L64\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/isDevMode\", \"name\": \"isDevMode\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"isdevmode\">isDevMode<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/isDevMode#isdevmode\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">experimental</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Returns whether Angular is in development mode. After called once,\nthe value is locked and won't change any more.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/core/isDevMode\" class=\"code-anchor\">isDevMode</a>(): boolean</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>boolean</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/isDevMode#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, this is true, unless a user calls <code><a href=\"api/core/enableProdMode\" class=\"code-anchor\">enableProdMode</a></code> before calling this.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/enableProdMode\n - api/core/isDevMode#description\n - api/core/isDevMode#isdevmode\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L52-L64\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L52-L64\n-->"
